BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "System Events"	tell dock preferences		set props to (get properties)		set loc to (get screen edge of props)				if (loc = bottom) then			set screen edge of props to left		else			set screen edge of props to bottom		end if				set properties to props	end tellend telldo shell script "killall Dock"

BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "System Preferences"	activate	set current pane to pane "com.apple.preference.trackpad"end telldelay 1tell application "System Events"	tell process "System Preferences"		click radio button 2 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 1 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 2 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 3 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 4 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 1 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 2 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 3 of tab group 1 of window 1		click checkbox 4 of tab group 1 of window 1	end tellend telltell application "System Preferences"	quitend tell
